name: Composer
description:
Composer v0.5

As I kept working on my other model (NSFW), I realized I wanted something more artistic while keeping that cinematic, realistic feel and thus created this model.

This model is a work in progress using the latest stable diffusion techniques to bring the most vibrant colors in a cinematic, artistic style with high details. With the right prompt and high-res fix, you can create some amazing images.

I'm looking for feedback to improve this model, so please share your thoughts constructively so I can make a better version for the community.
